## Quick Reference

**Entry points:** New project | Discover existing project | Generate document | Check traceability | Generate full package | Publish

**Generation order:** VP → URS → Risk Assessment → FS → DS → IQ → OQ → PQ

**Modes:** Coached (interactive refinement) or Fast Draft (complete package, minimal interruption)

**Manifest:** `docs/v-model/v-model-manifest.json` — single source of truth for project state

**Scripts:**
- `python scripts/init_project.py --name "..." --description "..." --gamp-category 4 --regulatory-context 21_CFR_11,annex_11 --audience mixed`
- `python scripts/traceability_check.py --manifest docs/v-model/v-model-manifest.json`
- `python scripts/publish_docx.py --input docs/v-model/fs.md --manifest docs/v-model/v-model-manifest.json`
- `python scripts/import_discovery.py --answers discovery-answers.json --manifest docs/v-model/v-model-manifest.json`

Always read `@SKILL.md` first for the complete workflow and coaching tone guidance.
